description: Exceptional Seaport Loft featuring oversized industrial windows and charming brick-and-beam details. The open-concept kitchen offers ample storage, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish island/bar—perfect for entertaining. The spacious bedroom, complete with a sliding door entry, is thoughtfully designed for privacy. Enjoy generous closet and storage space, soaring 11-foot ceilings, and original Carolina sandblasted beams. The large bathroom includes an attached laundry area for added convenience. This well-established building boasts a central location near top restaurants, shops, and public transportation. One garage parking space included.
